  "detailed_description": "<strong>Artificial Life Simulator</strong> is a relaxing and colorful simulation game where you create artificial life forms based on particle interactions. The particles interact with each other through forces, resulting in unique emergent behaviors.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805670/extras/9beaf9d1e8e1b7fdedc2deea3e4391d3.avif?t=1773313044\" width=600 height=85 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Explore unique artificial universes in 3D or 2D.<br></li><li> The user interface can be hidden for a more immersive experience. This is also useful if you want to take screenshots or record a video.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805670/extras/746fcc7b0282a00e67eb3230df1823a9.poster.avif?t=1773313044\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805670/extras/746fcc7b0282a00e67eb3230df1823a9.webm?t=1773313044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805670/extras/746fcc7b0282a00e67eb3230df1823a9.mp4?t=1773313044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805670/extras/7ec3e6283ffa9fc589cfbf1541397cff.avif?t=1773313044\" width=600 height=85 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Create your own simulations easily with up to eight different particle colors.<br></li><li> Each particle can exert attractive and repulsive forces on the other particle colors.<br></li><li> The simulations can be saved to the computer so you can keep the simulations that you find interesting.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805670/extras/5629838c9d53e43e21d2de578ce5a018.poster.avif?t=1773313044\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805670/extras/5629838c9d53e43e21d2de578ce5a018.webm?t=1773313044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805670/extras/5629838c9d53e43e21d2de578ce5a018.mp4?t=1773313044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805670/extras/d66273e01274899dbe4a8426da25f8a4.avif?t=1773313044\" width=600 height=85 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Simulations can be randomized which can yield unexpected results and help you discover new artificial life forms!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805670/extras/44c18ab1817c446b32cdcb08e521ed5d.poster.avif?t=1773313044\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805670/extras/44c18ab1817c446b32cdcb08e521ed5d.webm?t=1773313044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805670/extras/44c18ab1817c446b32cdcb08e521ed5d.mp4?t=1773313044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805670/extras/7695b08ad33922009177e196cb5c6c55.avif?t=1773313044\" width=600 height=85 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Adjust different simulation settings while the simulation is running. The settings can have a large impact on how the simulation evolves!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805670/extras/dec37a4999078482a6214fec876557f4.poster.avif?t=1773313044\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805670/extras/dec37a4999078482a6214fec876557f4.webm?t=1773313044\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805670/extras/dec37a4999078482a6214fec876557f4.mp4?t=1773313044\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This game is heavily inspired by Jeffrey Ventrella's \"Clusters\" and \"Boids\" by Craig Reynolds.<br><br>The game uses compute shaders which might not be possible to run on older hardware. Please try out the demo before purchasing the full game.",
